00:04:56.240 --> 00:05:03.160
 Ancient time, so many of those great masters who reached high realization, but at the beginning

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:05.240
 time, they went to so many challenges.

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:10.840
 It is difficult to one up or another. Even when they are growing time in the families, one up or

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:11.640
 another.

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:20.140
 But that pushed them so much, brought strong courage and commitment, confidence and determination

00:05:20.140 --> 00:05:29.340
 to explore the meaning of very distressed lives, to benefit themselves, to all the beings.

00:05:29.340 --> 00:05:37.060
 Wide kindness, compassion, love, that's what we received teaching from the great master, the Buddha

00:05:37.060 --> 00:05:37.240
.

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:39.240
 That's really the teaching.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:44.540
 So it's really both that spiritual and dharmic qualities in the heart and mind.

00:05:44.540 --> 00:05:51.380
 So therefore, we should not be totally kind of like discipline and upset, but raise up our spirit

00:05:51.380 --> 00:05:57.540
 and courage and commitment and held our heads high.

00:05:57.540 --> 00:06:01.440
